{"type": "article", "id": 5960, "title": "Alki 2015 家具新品", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-06T07:33:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233856bdhWSJORfCrIDH4N.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t法国设计师家居品牌 Alki 在今年的巴黎国际家居装饰博览会上发布了 2015 新品。 Kuskoa Bi 是目前市面上出现的首款由生物塑料材质制作而成的椅子，搭配以实木椅腿；Zutik 是一个实心橡木材质的墙面搁架系统，提供不同长度的灵活组合方式；此外，另有 Jantzi 、Hiruki 与  Heldu 3 款实心橡木座椅与核桃木制成的 EMBA 系列吧椅。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233853vcz46MtHy5L3fqAI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233854I3ZTfn0BhkYGXJbC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7109375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523385412JcObhTrXxpEL0y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.884375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233855NEUOSft1kJ2cQXIL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233855rb4uj0mKwcNfLvyP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}